────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
[STEP 1b] ARCHITECTURE MISMATCH — BUILD ON SERVER
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Problem : devcontainer is arm64, server is amd64 (x86_64)
Error   : exec /usr/local/bin/docker-php-entrypoint: exec format error

Solution: Build image directly on the server using nerdctl + buildkitd

Commands executed on server (46.62.135.86):
  # 1. Transfer source code
  tar czf /tmp/hello-agent-src.tar.gz -C brama-agents/hello-agent .
  scp /tmp/hello-agent-src.tar.gz root@46.62.135.86:/tmp/

  # 2. Extract on server
  mkdir -p /tmp/hello-agent-build
  tar xzf /tmp/hello-agent-src.tar.gz -C /tmp/hello-agent-build

  # 3. Build with nerdctl (uses buildkitd, produces native amd64 image)
  nerdctl --namespace k8s.io build -t brama/hello-agent:dev /tmp/hello-agent-build/

  # 4. Import into K3S containerd
  nerdctl --namespace k8s.io save brama/hello-agent:dev | k3s ctr images import -

Result  : SUCCESS
Image   : docker.io/brama/hello-agent:dev (sha256:e017de4d0798...)
Arch    : linux/amd64
Size    : 215.3 MiB (in K3S containerd)

